name: NFT Collector Badge 2021
description:
This is a fun made Collector Badge in 2 Versions for 2021. You can have one or more for fun and for future use. Next generations will be more complex and elaborate. Since 2021 every year new badges will emerge. It is not mandatory to own one but if you do it will also help our purpose. If you can't afford one please contact us on twitter and we will provide you with one piece. NFT space is fun and engaging, so do we! Enjoy.

Own a piece of history
